fin

Bored of looking at all the personal finance management softwares, I decided to write a simple one to manage my personal finance software. This will help storing my finance and also learn a bit of statistics to mine my personal finance.

What we need

A list of expenditures (one that can extended by the user)
list of transaction

Database
---------

Transaction:
TID
Date
Comment
Tag (Type of expenditure) -> 1 to 1 foreign key to Tags

Tags: 
TagID
Description
